Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,「真正的解脱　是尚未能出生之人的特权
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,「一旦呱呱坠地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,「就只能在无数的波及中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,「永远不得安宁」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你父亲雾间诚一的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多也可以告诉我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,五年前事件的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那件事我之前也说过的吧　那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.77,0:02:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,「那是不吉波普干的」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,还要说这种都市传说糊弄我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法从五年前那件事件的「波及」中逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你不也是这样吗　雾间同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你对那次事件...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,家父的书还是别读的好　末真同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.07,0:02:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一个月前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,F 班的百合原美奈子和高一的早乙女正美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.11,0:02:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,二人一同失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这起事件也和你有关的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪的彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,最近经常看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那个不是彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我看啊　肯定还是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,死神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不吉波普？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,当真？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你想啊　1 班的男生不也消失了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哦哦哦　城之内？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好像都向警方提出搜索请求了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,听说他是和父亲两人一起生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么看　帕纳鲁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.35,0:03:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不吉波普　存不存在呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不吉波普　大概是存在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不过就算真的存在　对这个世界也没有影响
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,要不咱们去卡啦OK吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:03:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,想去想去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,矢部　顺路去趟游艺厅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,啊抱歉　今天不行　我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一起去呗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我赶时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,明天教训他一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛都要看直啦　帕纳鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,哦〜　你看上人家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什么　帕纳鲁　真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌　才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别瞎说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,美铃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,阳子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒啊阳子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这次模拟考也是第一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,城之内同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,城之内同学　还没被找到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　确实啊　真让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉有些不好受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:05:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,自从城之内同学失踪起就一直...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,阳子　原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像有什么重要的东西... 被城之内同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的　阳子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.93,0:05:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,美铃...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,天空好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,已经到冬天了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,美铃真是怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你什么都能包容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,只要和美铃聊几句　就会感觉自己的烦恼真是太蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,美铃真是品格高尚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不过啊美铃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你被人叫做「帕纳鲁」呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不是品格高尚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,爱着这个世界而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,帕纳鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是的　我热爱这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,热爱它　肯定它　包容它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,而教给我这些的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,就是她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,接受这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,接受丧失　接受混沌　包容一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,森田警官　你按住那边！{ep4}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,喂　给我老实点儿！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,理惠...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,理惠...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,理惠...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,理惠...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,别挣扎了　老实点！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,世界只是如此存在着{本集VIP}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,无论什么事都有可能发生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,而...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,而发生的事情都是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,正因有悲伤痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,才更要热爱这个世界　肯定这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我的感情从未被扰乱过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我将这个世界的一切照搬全收地接受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,帕纳鲁...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我要买这些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,请把其中一张包装成礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,目前车辆发生故障
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,为探明故障原因　将暂时停车
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉耽误各位旅客的宝贵时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,呼唤我的是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你呼唤的我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？为什么你可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么人？和早乙女正美一样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不　还是说...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,对了　你的脑...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,脑子有你的记忆... 那里的构造是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊这样啊这样啊这样啊这样啊这样啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,等我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这是「GOD IS DEAD」乐队的新曲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,帕纳鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此　她就是帕纳鲁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经包容接受了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你爱着这个任何事都可能发生的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,人类真是怪异
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,无聊的思想竟连接上了特殊的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你想将「世界爱」推广开来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,将帕纳鲁对世界的爱传播给更多人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他到底是什么人　都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他是除我之外第一个理解了帕纳鲁思想的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,美铃　我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,从那之后就越来越不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.51,0:12:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,城之内同学... 我被城之内同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你见一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人是阳子的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,前段时间阳子不是说我什么都能包容的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,阳子　你也可以变成那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？真能让我轻松起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,像城之内同学对我做的那样...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他有他的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,推广帕纳鲁的世界爱的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,笹冈？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,阳子还没享受到许诺好的幸福　就这样逝去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不过　这也是世界的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧　帕纳鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这种地方做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我呆在这里　有什么不行的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种诡异的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你一个人居然还能待得住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你是圣谷的学生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你们学校这几天不是刚有学生失踪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,失踪...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说城之内同学吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,关于他这个人　你知道些什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,先行告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我想城之内同学　肯定是没能爱上这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,爱上世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你不要再来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这里对我来说　是个重要的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的场所啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这里啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,雾间凪...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才那个女的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.57,0:14:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,雾间凪...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,也有必要将「世界爱」宣教给她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,叫她出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.84,0:14:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她会来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定会来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:14:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你就打电话　这样说...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是说了吗　是早乙女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,早乙女正美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他说有话要跟你讲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,早乙女正美...！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在　你就是我们的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,喂？雾间同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以接近那家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,别管那么多！总之...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们负有对你宣教「世界爱」的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,所以　一定要来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,她会来吗？雾间同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,会来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,早乙女正美的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是用来钓她的最好的诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,诱饵啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉像在做什么坏事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:16:00.68,Top,,0,0,0,,没错　而诱饵就是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在你们的传闻中　我被为死神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,喂　早乙女　这个人...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,早乙女？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是早乙女正美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的早乙女正美已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是你杀了早乙女？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你为那家伙的实体化提供了「场」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你在袒护「世界之敌」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我说啊　死神小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们才不是世界之敌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,而是正相反
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是真正的帕纳鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你的「世界爱」和帕纳鲁的「世界爱」截然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,当你替换了真正的帕纳鲁的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你的命运就已经定下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:16:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,才...才不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我将帕纳鲁的世界爱继承了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,然后... 然后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我　帕纳鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,美铃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不要为这种事哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,可是... 那你说　为什么我们要出生？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么非得活下去？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得是为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说啊　我就是不知道这个呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,并没有什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.25,0:17:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,总之我们就是出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,而后存活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,世界只是如此存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不管我们多么痛苦　这都是我们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,正因有这些痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.62,0:17:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们才更加不得不爱这个世界　肯定这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个叫做「帕纳鲁」的人说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(398,516)}Paneloux
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,帕纳鲁？他是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,保密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哎　帕纳鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样叫我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么嘛　这是在尊敬你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我想听更多关于帕纳鲁的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,关于这个世界　关于爱　关于肯定　还有更多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,明天再约会吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,放学后老地方　我在北口公园等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不管我们多么痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是我们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂了　帕纳鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她成了那时连续猎奇杀人事件的受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而你...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我继承了帕纳鲁的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我将世界的一切照搬全收地接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你所包容的并不是世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而是她的死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你从帕纳鲁那里没有继承任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是为了在这个世界中保护自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,假装自己爱着世界而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,而你的「爱」为他提供了恰合适的「场」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你那不成样的进化　让那家伙实体化了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,进化？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,彩虹消失了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.29,0:20:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,实在没办法啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不这样的话我就活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我还能怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个荒谬的世界里　该怎样活下去？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,带我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,就像城之内同学那样　把我带走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不带你走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉　你毫无让我带走的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.49,0:20:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不吉波普...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,将我从这个世界中拯救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,谁快来救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,警察叔叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我！求你救救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真让我惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.13,0:21:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,世界只是如此存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,无论什么事都有可能发生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,而发生的事情都是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子
Comment: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,·Preview·
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.32,0:23:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}约会？怎么可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.02,0:23:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谁管你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.38,0:23:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你谁啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:26.69,Top,,0,0,0,,用了这个就能改变自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.32,0:23:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,还要约会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.69,0:23:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:28.50,Top,,0,0,0,,变得大胆起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.69,0:23:29.38,Top,,0,0,0,,{\an9}理惠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.02,0:23:30.53,Top,,0,0,0,,{\an7}求你了　别告诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:30.57,Top,,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.60,0:23:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}要约会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:33.82,Top,,0,0,0,,我把你的那份用掉了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.54,0:23:31.97,Top,,0,0,0,,{\an9}理惠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我有女友的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.90,0:23:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}你只能吃蔬菜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.05,0:23:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我穿得合身吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.21,0:23:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}不许看... 不许看！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}为了重塑人类社会　是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.67,0:23:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}理惠只属于我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:40.67,Top,,0,0,0,,要是你又想要了　就随时再到这个地方来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.62,0:23:39.15,Top,,0,0,0,,{\an9}理惠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那接下来教你什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:40.20,Top,,0,0,0,,{\an9}理惠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.26,0:23:41.20,Top,,0,0,0,,{\an9}理惠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.46,0:23:43.06,Top,,0,0,0,,帕纳鲁是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.51,0:23:43.25,Top,,0,0,0,,{\an9}理惠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.33,0:23:45.27,Top,,0,0,0,,嗯　帕纳鲁就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.34,0:23:44.22,Top,,0,0,0,,{\an9}理惠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.47,0:23:45.28,Top,,0,0,0,,{\an9}理惠
